urlText: Dubbo XPT will operate to an amended timetable
content:
Due to extensive damage to the Blue Mountains Line as a result of recent bush fires between Mount Victoria and Lithgow
This service will operate to an amended timetable Tuesday to Sunday, connections to and from North and Southern regions can not be guaranteed during this time. Monday XPT services will be replaced by a road coach service.
